  "detailed_description": "Drive a kart on different locations in first person driver view only.  Try to beat the race time of other players and put your name in the highscore list.  To be faster you can configurate different settings of your kart. You will see your last round time in game on the steering wheel once you finished a round. Every engine power class has its own highscore.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1376360/extras/65a7ecd8c9f4644c28f6b53247073e49.poster.avif?t=1705517196\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1376360/extras/65a7ecd8c9f4644c28f6b53247073e49.webm?t=1705517196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1376360/extras/65a7ecd8c9f4644c28f6b53247073e49.mp4?t=1705517196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can drive with keyboard (WASD or Arrow keys , R restart track ,   1-9 for radio , /*-+ for volume control, ESC for go back to menue). Its a development focus that you can drive good with keyboard. Steering Wheel + Force Feedback and Gamepads are supported.",
